# Set the random seed
    random.seed(seed)

    # Initialize the arrays to store the outcomes and frequencies
    outcomes = np.zeros(6, dtype=np.int32)
    frequencies = np.zeros(6, dtype=np.int32)

    # Simulate the rolls and calculate the frequencies
    for _ in range(rolls):
        value = random.choice(NUMBERS)
        outcomes[value - 1] += 1
        frequencies[value - 1] += 1

    # Convert the frequencies to probabilities
    probabilities = frequencies / rolls

    # Create the Axes object and plot the histogram
    plt.title("Histogram of Dice Rolls")
    plt.xlabel("Dice Value")
    plt.ylabel("Frequency")
    plt.bar(np.arange(1, 7), frequencies, align="center", color="red")
    plt.show()

    return (outcomes, frequencies, probabilities, ax)
